<br>
I try to avoid the frustration by avoiding the uncompletable quests.  If the mob is up, sure i will go kill it, but i won't sit around for week in once zone, skipping meals, not sleeping so i can be there when he pops.  That is just not my idea of fun.  There are plenty of fun things to do without hitting yourself in the head with a hammer.<br>
