<br>
Got the standard answer everytime.  petiton it.  With which I replied, &quot;which time?&quot;  Anyone who has petitioned before knows you only get 1 in the que.  So to put in 3 says they either ignored or deleted it.  It took about 2 minutes to actually do and 7 online hours to bug the crap out of them to get them to actually do it.<br>
<br>
Imagine taking your car to the repair shop and placing a down payment.  Now add that calls for it for the next few days when it was promised that afternoon still doesn't get your car fixed.  Better yet, you get it out of the shop and it is still broke down, but they reply it's working as intended.  Ask yourself if you would ever take your car there ever again... if you had the option?<br>
<br>
I'm also one of those weening myself off the EQ crack addition. <p>Lacki Dasmacki<BR>
